title: 'bridges: remove dead FloatJsonValueMetric'

doc:
- audience: Node Dev
  description: |-
    Removes the unused `FloatJsonValueMetric` from `relay-utils`. It fetched a
    token price over HTTP (CoinGecko) via `isahc` to compute cross-chain message
    fees, but that mechanism was removed in parity-bridges-common#1642 and the
    type has been dead code since. Dropping it removes the `isahc -> curl ->
    openssl-sys` dependency chain from the bridges relay tree.

crates: []
